Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Subfinder not found after installation

Solution: Ensure ~/go/bin is in your PATH. Run source ~/.bashrc or restart terminal.
Issue: No subdomains discovered

Solution: Try a different domain (e.g., tesla.com, hackerone.com). Some domains have limited public subdomains.
Issue: Waybackurls returns no results

Solution: The domain may not have archived data. Try well-established domains with long history.
Issue: Python script fails with import errors

Solution: Install missing packages: pip3 install requests waybackpy
Issue: Permission denied when running scripts

Solution: Make scripts executable: chmod +x script_name.py
